Item

Class MoneyItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • Utility.Entity
        • Item.Item
          • Item.MoneyItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class MoneyItem
extends Item
    MoneyItem extends Item and has a instance variabel for money value. MoneyItem is a somewhat unique item as it contains a value that is used to update the player’s money and is not added to the player’s inventory array list when added.

    0.1
